'''Hickton''' is the master of [[Fletching]], and resides in a two-story building near the [[bank]] in central [[Catherby]]. Hickton also owns an archery supplies shop called [[Hickton's Archery Emporium]]. Players with [[Skill mastery|level 99]] in Fletching may buy a [[Fletching cape]] from Hickton. To purchase the cape, players have to access [[Hickton's Archery Emporium]] by trading him to see the cape being sold for 99,000 [[coins]].

==Treasure Trails==
{{Anagram|Hickton|medium|THICKNO}}. The answer to his challenge: ''How many ranges are there in Catherby?'' is: ''2''.

